OL,3,CBelfast stabbing victim out of induced
OL,4,Ccoma, family say
OL,6,FBelfast stabbing victim Stephen
OL,7,FOgilvie is out of an induced coma, his
OL,8,Ffamily have confirmed.
OL,10,FMr Ogilvie lost his left eye and
OL,11,Fsuffered deep cuts to his head, face
OL,12,Fand back in a knife attack in north
OL,13,FBelfast last Monday.
OL,15,FThe attack sparked a wave of protests
OL,16,Fand disorder in Northern Ireland.
OL,18,FMr Ogilivie's parents said their son's
OL,19,Frecovery is continuing but he faces
OL,20,Fthe 'possibility' of losing sight in
OL,21,Fhis other eye.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
