OL,3,CBelfast stabbing victim out of induced
OL,4,Ccoma, family say
OL,6,FHadi Alodid, 30, has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe attack. He has also been charged
OL,9,Fwith possession of a knife in a public
OL,10,Fplace, and with threatening to kill an
OL,11,FNHS radiographer.
OL,13,FA fundraiser in support of Mr Ogilvie
OL,14,Fhas raised more than #30,000,
OL,15,Fincluding a #10,000 donation from
OL,16,F'hurl hero' Maitiu Mag Tighearnan, who
OL,17,Fbravely intervened during the attack.
OL,26,@xD@UrpxD@`rp
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
