PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781783276
OL,3,CBelfast stabbing victim out of induced
OL,4,Ccoma, family say
OL,6,F"The funds raised will help provide
OL,7,FStephen with the equipment, support,
OL,8,Fand everyday items he may need as he
OL,9,Fadjusts to life following this attack.
OL,11,F"With the loss of sight in his left
OL,12,Feye and the possibility of losing
OL,13,Fsight in his right eye, your
OL,14,Fgenerosity will make a real difference
OL,15,Fto his future quality of life.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
